產者，依前\r\n項之規定處斷。\r\n前二項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c1292%2c20220614%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPDM,111,簡,1292,20220614,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"1292","JDATE":"20220614","JTITLE":"竊盜"}